<div class="card card-position">
  <div class="card-body">
    <div class="container conteiner-card">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-2">
          <%= image_tag position.company.logo, alt: "Logo marca da empresa #{position.company.name}", class: 'card-img-top'%>
        </div>
        <div class="col-10">
          <h4><%= position.name %></h4>
          <h5><%= "#{I18n.t('activerecord.attributes.position.careers')[position.career.to_sym]} - #{position.city} - #{I18n.t('activerecord.attributes.position.contracts')[position.contract.to_sym]}" %></h5>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Totam officia porro ab, nihil quis earum ratione repudiandae, ipsam neque quidem iusto commodi ipsum dolor cumque repellat fugiat corporis voluptatibus eaque.</p>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm mt-3">
              <button class="btn btn-danger" type="button">Ver mais</button>
              <button class="btn btn-success" type="button">Candidatar-se</button>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm text-right mt-3 group-social-network">
              <%= link_to image_tag('social-network/linkedin.svg', alt: 'Icone do LinkedIn', height: '32', width: '32'), "https://www.linkedin.com/sharing/share-offsite/?url=#{url_position(position)}", target: "_blank" %>
              <%= link_to image_tag('social-network/whatsapp.svg', alt: 'Icone do Whatsapp', height: '32', width: '32'), "https://wa.me/?text=#{text_position(position)}", target: "_blank" %>
              <%= link_to image_tag('social-network/twitter.svg', alt: 'Icone do Twitter', height: '32', width: '32'), "https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=#{text_position(position)}", target: "_blank" %>
              <%= link_to image_tag('social-network/copy.svg', alt: 'Icone do copiar', height: '32', width: '32', class: 'share-copy-icon'), '#', class: 'copy-url', data: { 'clipboard-text': url_position(position) } %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
